nodes.text: Verónica Segura is a Mexican actress who played the handmaiden Cordé in Star Wars: Episode II Attack of the Clones.
Besides Attack of the Clones, she has appeared in such films as Tribe, Subterano, Dame tu Cuerpo, Club Dread, and A Proposito de Alexa.
